name: don`t be afraid to be
description:
capitalizing on feelings
 this work was very healing for me, and I am here selling it as a crypto-work.
This makes me think many things that I will not describe here. However, here I am selling this, because art is not only my emotional containment, but it is also my way of making an economic profit in this difficult task of making a living from what I am passionate about.

1080 x 1080 

300 dpi
